Usage: PopClock [options]

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -m MESSAGE, --message=MESSAGE
                        Blink your message on the top of the clock
  -c COLOR, --color=COLOR
                        Set the message color
  -s SOUNDFILE, --soundfile=SOUNDFILE
                        Will play this file at startup
  -f, --fullscreen      Show the clock on fullscreen
  -t, --timeline        Show the Sprint Timeline (need to config wikipage)
  -e EXITAT, --exitat=EXITAT
                        Minutes to auto close (default 5 minutes)
  -d, --debug           Output debug messages
  -a, --alarm           Blink a red background
